You have been assigned to develop a software catalog of products where each product
is described by name, type, manufacturer, model, color, and price. Each product also
has an unique identifier.

Your software should let the user to add or remove products from the catalog, modify
the stock of each product in the catalog, modify the price of the product in the catalog,
get the current stock of a product in the catalog, and get the current price of a product
in the catalog. The software should also let the user to get a list of products from the 
catalog that match certain attributes of the products. 

Design all the objects, their attributes and methods, and the association among 
the objects.